title: RGIP: It's Curtains for Paris
description: Real Girlfriends in Paris has drawn to a close with a dramatic drapery installation, a slip dress reveal, and a meltdown on the Seine. We desperately hope this show comes back, but if it doesn't.... we'll always have Paris.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
